title: Hardware Monitor for U3 (Version 1.0.6)
description:
This is the latest version of Hardware Monitor from CPUID repackaged into a U3 install file.  This great little utility will monitor all system resources (like CPU, Graphics, HDD, Fans, etc.) that have sensors (temp., volt., etc.) for optimal performance...

More info: <a href=" http://cpuid.com/hwmonitor.php" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://cpuid.com/hwmonitor.php</a>
